    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained with no expense spared. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single blemish, and the interior is pristine, featuring premium materials that look and feel brand new. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
